faqs.question: What is a hackathon?
faqs.answer: A hackathon is an event where individuals or teams come together to collaboratively develop innovative solutions to specific challenges within a limited timeframe. It's a great opportunity to showcase your skills, learn from others, and create something impactful.

faqs.question: Who can participate?
faqs.answer: Our hackathon is open to anyone passionate about technology and innovation! Whether you're a seasoned developer, designer, entrepreneur, or a student eager to explore the world of tech, you're welcome to join us.

faqs.question: How do I register for the hackathon?
faqs.answer: Registration is simple! Visit our website and click on the 'Register' button. Fill out the registration form with your details and team information if applicable. Once registered, you'll receive a confirmation email with further instructions.

faqs.question: Do I need to have a team to participate?
faqs.answer: Teams are encouraged but not mandatory. You can register as an individual, and we'll help you find like-minded participants to form a team. Alternatively, if you already have a team, you can register together.

faqs.question: What are the themes or challenges of the hackathon?
faqs.answer: The hackathon will feature a variety of themes and challenges spanning different areas such as sustainability, healthcare, fintech, education, and more. Participants can choose which challenge aligns best with their interests and expertise.

faqs.question: What do I need to bring to the hackathon?
faqs.answer: Bring your laptop, charger, any necessary software or development tools, and a mindset ready to innovate! We'll provide Wi-Fi, meals, and any other amenities needed during the event.

faqs.question: What happens if I don't have a project idea?
faqs.answer: Don't worry! We'll have ideation sessions and mentors available to help you brainstorm and refine your ideas. You can also join a team with an existing idea that aligns with your skills and interests.

faqs.question: Will there be prizes?
faqs.answer: Yes! We'll have exciting prizes for winning teams based on creativity, technical execution, and overall impact of the projects developed during the hackathon.

faqs.question: Can I attend the hackathon remotely?
faqs.answer: Depending on the event format, we may offer remote participation options. Check our website or contact us for more details closer to the event date.

faqs.question: How can I contact the organizers if I have more questions?
faqs.answer: For any further questions or inquiries, feel free to reach out to us via email at hackathon@example.com or through our social media channels. We're here to help!
